---
// Asegúrate de que este nombre coincida con tu archivo en 'public/'
const CV_URL = "/CV_Adrian_Gallardo.pdf"; 
const TU_EMAIL = "tu-email@gmail.com";
---
<section id="contacto" class="py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
  <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
    Hablemos
  </h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
    Estoy buscando activamente mi estancia profesional. Me encantaría conectar y discutir cómo puedo contribuir a tu equipo.
  </p>

  <a 
    href={CV_URL} 
    download="CV_Adrian_Gallardo_Desarrollador.pdf" 
    class="bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg inline-block mb-12"
  >
    Descargar mi CV
  </a>

  <form 
    name="contact" 
    method="POST" 
    data-netlify="true" 
    class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-left"
  >
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
    
    <div class="mb-4">
      <label for="name" class="block text-gray-300 mb-2">Tu Nombre</label>
      <input 
        type="text" 
        name="name" 
        id="name" 
        required 
        class="w-full p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cyan-500"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="mb-4">
      <label for="email" class="block text-gray-300 mb-2">Tu Email</label>
      <input 
        type="email" 
        name="email" 
        id="email" 
        required 
        class="w-full p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cyan-500"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="mb-4">
      <label for="message" class="block text-gray-300 mb-2">Mensaje</label>
      <textarea 
        name="message" 
        id="message" 
        rows="4" 
        required 
        class="w-full p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cyan-500"
      ></textarea>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
      <button 
        type="submit" 
        class="bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white font-medium py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors w-full sm:w-auto"
      >
        Enviar Mensaje
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 mt-12">

    <a 
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adrian-gallardo-27913a390/" 
      target="_blank" 
      rel="noopener noreferrer" 
      class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors"
    >
      LinkedIn
    </a>
    <a 
      href="https://github.com/Novarton" 
      target="_blank" 
      rel="noopener noreferrer" 
      class="text-gray-400 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors"
    >
      GitHub
    </a>
  </div>
</section>